-- IfW Says 80% Greek Bond Losses Are Needed, Boersen Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-01-25T07:17:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-25/ifw-says-80-greek-bond-losses-are-needed-boersen-reports.html
The IfW economic research institute,
based in Kiel,  Germany , said  Greece  needs private investors to
take losses on government bond holdings of more than 80 percent
if the country is to stabilize its budget,  Boersen-Zeitung 
reported, citing a study by the institute.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
